Key extra items: OPD Block expansion, elevated water tank shifting, fire safety additions.

Clause Relied Upon: CPWD GCC Clause 12 (Extra Items), Clause 12A (Variation Rates)
TOTAL CLAIM 2: ₹6.15 Crore (as per joint measurements and agreed rate analysis)

Evidence: 11 Variation Orders, Joint Measurement Books, Rate Analysis approved by EE.
