(a) Award a total sum of ₹19.84 Crore with interest @ 12% p.a. from 15.01.2026 till realization.
(b) Declare the termination dated 15.01.2026 as illegal and void.
(c) Direct release of Security Deposit and Performance Guarantee.
(d) Grant Extension of Time of 8 months.
(e) Award cost of arbitration proceedings.

